          <p>When the interaction effect is small, we can derive a simpler expression using the approximations e<italic><sup>x</sup></italic>&#x2212;1&#x2248;<italic>x</italic>, and <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="gepi0035-0278-mu18.jpg" mimetype="image"/></inline-formula>,</p>
