          <p>The reciprocal of this is the asymptotic variance of the MLE of &#x3B2;, <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="gepi0035-0278-mu27.jpg" mimetype="image"/></inline-formula>. The Wald test statistic for &#x3B2; asymptotically follows a <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="gepi0035-0278-mu28.jpg" mimetype="image"/></inline-formula> distribution with noncentrality parameter <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="gepi0035-0278-mu29.jpg" mimetype="image"/></inline-formula>. Therefore,</p>
